source.en: Blaser, Magdalena "Myths of the Cofán people"

sentences.text: Fae coenza tsu canse tise dushundeccu coemba puiyi'cco pushepa ja'fasi tisuyi.
Tsa a'i can'jeinte'ta te avuve metssi.
Tsa'ma tsa coenza Terere qquen inise'chota'te avu quini'jima atesucho.
Tise dutssi'yembe dushundeccu qquipae'su'fasi tise yayandeccuja vacho'vai'ccu vacho'su ja'fa, tsa'ma ni fae'ccoeyi'qque indi'fambi.
Tsa'ma Terere ja'ta, tsai'mbi'tssi avuve indiji.
Tsa'caen indijipa ipa an.
Tsa'caen tise yayaccashe'ye an'jensi tise du'shumbe dushundeccuja afeya qquen in'jamba ronda'jenga'fa.
Tsa'ma tsa a'ija tisuyi pa'ccoma an'jen.
Tsa'caen tise'panga afembe tisuyi ansi dushundeccuja tise'pa yayani japa su'fa: Yayaccashe'yeta tsu avuma an'jen, que'qque avuma indi'ngaja añe.
Tsa'caen susi japa vachopa ni fae avuveyi'qque indi'fambi.
Tansie fae metoracho'ccoeyi indi'fa.
Tsa'ma tise'pa yayaccashe'ye ja'ta ñocca'e avuma panzapa ji'je.
Tsa'cansi tise du'shumbe dushundeccuja ro'ndapa atteye in'jan'fa micomba tise'yi avuma panza'je'choma.
Tsa'camba tise avu vacho'su jayisi sepaccoe omboen'fa.
Tsa'caen tise vacho'vama isupa jayisi sepaccoe ombaemba tsampi enttingeningae japa naini ja'fambi.
Tsa'caen jayipa tise ccumba suvaen'ccoma shonchhan jayi.
Shon'chhan jasi japa atte'fa avuma indi'je'choma.
Tsampini fae quini'jin ccutsu'choja avupa.
Terereja tse'jinga catsepa tise ccumbama sutsapa ccumba onfen'bai'ccu ufa, cuintsu avu andeye.
Tsa'caen tsonsi injantssi avu sefane tsa quini'jiñe ande'fa.
Andesi tise vacho'vai'ccu ttovapa avuma indi.
Tsa'caen indipa ipa tsama pa'ccoma sho'ccaemba ni fae'ccoe'qque afambe pa'ccoma tisuyi an.
Afembe tisuyi ansi tise dushundeccuja iyicca'ye'fa.
Iyicca'yepa bopa condasepa ñoña'fa ma'caen rande coyeccuve toñe.
Tsomba coyema injan'tsse jon'baen'fa.
Jonsi coye sho'yopa coemba namba cu'cho.
Tsa'caen namba cu'chosi dushundeccuja tisu'pa yayama anga'je'fa coye cu'choma iye.
Tsa'caen tson'jen'fa'choma attepa tsa ccashe'yeja qquepa su: Ñama'qque a'faseja ña'qque japa cu'choma ipa matssamba añe.
Qquen su'choma pañamba japa tise'pa yayandeccunga conda'fa.
Tsonsi su'fa: Tisu japa cu'choma in'gapa añe su'faja.
Ccashe'ye coyeccuningae jasi tise dushundeccuyi ccopayeve di'shapa ccoyeccuni ja'fa.
Tsa'caen japa coye cu'choma ttuttu furiamba isu'je'chonga napipa tise'nga bopa puifae quitsu'tsu tso'fema tssanjan'fa.
Tsa'caen tson'fasi Terereja tso'fe tssamba in'naa tsaoni napi.
Tsama tise du'shumbe dushundeccuja attepa tisu'pa yayandeccuni japa conda'fa.
Tsa'ma tsendeccuja pañamba su'fa: ¿Japa iñajampaña'faja jongoesumande dyojo?
Qquen susi pañamba tise'pa yayaccashe'yema iñajampaña'fa.
Yayaccashe'ye canjansi'o cundeye jiña'ninda mingae qui daya?
Tsama pañamba su: Canjansimanda gi dyojombi, micoña'mbi tsu.
Tsonsi ccase iñajampaña'fa.
¿Ttesi'o jiña'ninda mingae qui ccushaya?
Tsama'qque dyojombi'gi.
Qquen su'choma pañamba dushundeccuja japa tise'pa yayandeccunga condapa su'fa.
Yayaccashe'yeja dyojombi tsu.
Tsonsi ccase tise'pa yayandeccuja su'fa: ¿Ccase japa su'faja tana'on tsofema quitsu'tsuye jiña'ninda mingae qui tsoña?
Tsonsi japa iñajampaña'fa.
Tsonsi dyosi jipa su'fa: Tsa iñajampaña'chomajan ñoa'me tsu dyojo'ya yayaccashe'yeja.
Tsonsi tise'pa yayandeccuja manda'fa tisu'pa in'janqquia'caen.
Tsama pañamba japa canttini'cco chu'pama ucca'shopa tsambe ttonoccuma qque'shopa tsimi'cconga eji'jiamba jeña'fa.
Jeña'fasi faesundeccuja su'fa: Yayaccashe'ye, tanamo jiña'fa que tso'fema ccase quitsu'tsu tssañañe.
¿Mani gi anga'faya?
Qquen supa tive'ye fendepa anga'fa ccappoccufanga.
Tseni angapa va'tti tsu qquen supa ccapoccufanga coetta moen'fasi amppi ja.
Tise pa tsu in'jan'fa tsa'caen tsomba fi'ttiye.
Tsomba toya ccofetta moembi'te queja tsandave di'shapa canseja qquen supa ccofetta moen'fa piyiccufanga.
Tsa'caen fi'tti'fasi tsampini canse'chondeccu jipa bopa tsa avu quini'jima ttuttu'fa, cuintsu dushundeccu avuma amba quinsetsse coen'faye.
